{"id":320124,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-沈阳访民诉公安秘密拘留案开庭，多位旁/","date":"2013-10-28T14:34:52Z","modified":"2013-10-28T14:34:52Z","title":"维权网 | 沈阳访民诉公安秘密拘留案开庭，多位旁听访民遭控制（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span>(维权网信息员李军报道）2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日上午，沈阳访民许梅英诉和平区公安在两会期间秘密拘留一案在沈阳和平区法院开庭，多位沈阳维权人士、访民到法庭旁听。</span><br /><span> </span><span></span><br /><span>开庭后，法庭现场出现多位便衣人员，要没收旁听的沈阳访民辛颖、王振华的手机，辛颖多次表示自己的手机已经关机，仍然遭到拒绝，辛颖、王振华随后表示不再参加旁听，退出法庭。结果辛颖被强行带到了和平分局刑警大队新华刑侦中队限制人身自由，王振华也遭到了控制。参加旁听的访民杨蓓被带到新华派出所控制，期间报警</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>次近二小时无人接警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span><span></span><br /><span>法庭审理期间，等候在庭外的证人不让出庭作证，法庭上坐着</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个警察监视剩余旁听的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个人，和平法院门前聚集了大批各个派出所民警。</span><br /><span></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--VG7g-l8AQI/Um49MFvEWtI/AAAAAAAAqPA/XIp8GBy4xLM/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"255\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--VG7g-l8AQI/Um49MFvEWtI/AAAAAAAAqPA/XIp8GBy4xLM/s400/1.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span> </span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}